6 class="card-title"><strong>PHILLIP WALL</strong></h6> <p class="card-text"> Director | Worship <br>Email: <a class="text-info" href="mailto:phillip@livintegrity.org">phillip@livintegrity.org</a> </p></div></div><div class="card"> <img class="card-img-top" src="http://localhost:8888/integrity/public/img/leadership/StephenStaff.jpg" alt="Lead Pastor"> <div class="card-body bg-dark p-1"> <h6 class="card-title"><strong>STEPHEN PECKOUS</strong></h6> <p class="card-text"> Deacon | Member Care <br>Email: <a class="text-info" href="mailto:stephenpeckous@gmail.com">stephenpeckous@gmail.com</a> </p></div></div><div class="card"> <img class="card-img-top" src="http://localhost:8888/integrity/public/img/leadership/RayStaff.jpg" alt="Lead Pastor"> <div class="card-body bg-dark p-1"> <h6 class="card-title"><strong>RAY SHIMER</strong></h6> <p class="card-text"> Director | Finance <br>Email: <a class="text-info" href="mailto:rshimer@suddenlink.net">rshimer@suddenlink.net</a> </p></div></div></div>', null, 1, 1);
